cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.DL, cs.SI 

This paper discusses a platform that aims to provide a solution to internet censorship, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The platform is based on blockchain and peer-to-peer network, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of multi-chains architecture, which is related to distributed ledger technology (cs.DL) and system integration (cs.SI).
